+---------------+--------------------------------------------------+
|   rule check  |             在'if/for/while'后添加';'            |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------+
|    message    | Odd semicolon ';' after 'if/for/while' operator. |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------+

